snippet.title: Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion - Shivering Isles Trailer
snippet.description: Get one more blast of nostalgia before the Skyrim release with the official trailer for the epic Oblivion expansion pack "Shivering Isles." This was an amazing expansion pack which added over 30 hours of gameplay and an entire new world to the already awesome Oblivion. Horse armor not included.
